==評價==
本片獲得多為正面的評價，影評人主要稱讚動作場面和勞倫斯等演員的演出，儘管批評片商硬要將電影拆成兩部，但還是認為《飢餓遊戲》系列有著令人滿意的結局<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-reviews-critics-katniss-20151120-story.html|title=Katniss is the best reason to stick with 'The Hunger Games: Mockingjay -- Part 2,' reviews say|author=Tracy Brown|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2015-11-21|accessdate=2015-11-22|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927105057/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-reviews-critics-katniss-20151120-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度71%<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hunger_games_mockingjay_part_2/ |title=The Hunger Games: Mockingjay — Part 2 (2015) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-11-24 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423133459/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hunger_games_mockingjay_part_2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分65，整體評價尚可<ref name="MC">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hunger-games-mockingjay---part-2 |title=The Hunger Games: Mockingjay — Part 2 reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-11-24 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516223256/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hunger-games-mockingjay---part-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

